{{main|Sabrina (Genetic Apex 225)}}
Sabrina makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s first expansion, {{TCGP|Genetic Apex}}. When the player plays this card, the player's opponent must switch their Active Pokémon with a Benched Pokémon of their choice.

